\v 12 Cˀia⁴ nca³ je³coan³ je²-vi⁴, qui³jen³ ya⁴ Capernaum Jesús, cao⁴ na⁴-le⁴, cao⁴ ntsˀe⁴, cao⁴ cho⁴ta⁴-le⁴. To⁴jnco³jao² ni⁴čhjin³ tsa³ca³tio² nca³ ya⁴. 
\s1 Jesús si¹tsje³ yo⁴nco⁴ 
