\v 6 Cˀia⁴ nca³ Jesús tsa³ve³ nca³ ti¹qui³jna³ cho⁴ta⁴-ve⁴, coan³jin³-le⁴ nca³ nˀion¹ coa²tse³ nca³ ti¹mˀen³, cˀoi⁴qui³tso²-le⁴: A³ me³-li² nca³ coan⁴ntai³.  
\v 7 Qui³nchja⁴ xi³ ti¹mˀen³: Señor, tsin²-na³ cho⁴ta⁴xˀin⁴-jin² xi³ cˀoa⁴ncˀa³-na³, xi³ si⁴²ca²jna³ya³-na³ tanque cˀia⁴ nca³ ma³tin²ya³ na³nta¹-ve⁴. Tjen⁴ an³ nčhoa¹³ cja⁴ˀai¹ xi³ je³ji³tjo³jen³ya³ ti¹tjon²-na³.  
