\v 25 Ya⁴ tjio¹tˀa³-le⁴ cro²-le⁴ Jesús je² na⁴-le⁴ cao⁴ nti³chja³ na⁴-le⁴, María chjon⁴²-le⁴ Cleofas, cao⁴ María Magdalena.  
