\c 20  
\s1 Jesús ja³ˀa¹ya³-le⁴ 
\r (Mt. 28:1-10; Mr. 16:1-8; Lc. 24:1-12) 
\p  
\v 1 Cˀia⁴ ni⁴čhjin³ tai²nco⁴ nca³ je² María Magdalena ja³ˀai³ ya⁴ tsjo¹-ve⁴ nca³ ta⁴njion², nca³ ta⁴njion²ya³-sa³. Tsa³ve³ nca³ je³qui³tjo³xin² la⁴jao⁴-ve⁴.  
